Short:    Pinball Dreams patcher for 040/060 boards
Type:     game/patch
Author:   jffabre@ensica.fr (Jean-Francois Fabre)

Now the game works without problem on all 680x0 CPUs

PATCHES DONE:

- No need to disable the caches. This is done at bootup.
- A stupid protection removed (at 2 locations) that caused crashes on my A1260 board
- An unexpected level-6 interrupt caused the game to crash (Fixed)
- Quit key (ESC) during the menu.

